text: (upbeat music)
- Here at AWS Professional Services,

we help customers build
their business vision.
- The most exciting part of my job

is the variety of topic
that I have to address.
- I look at what they want to do,
I ask questions,
then I come up with a solution.

- I really longed for more
people-to-people interactions
in my day to day,
and that's exactly what Proserve offers.
- I am surrounded

by probably the best intellect
you can possibly imagine.

- I work with people who are
passionate about technology
and obsessed with customer success.
- There's always everything's changing,
so we need to keep up.
- AWS gives you an autonomy to grow,
to build your career,
and go wherever you want to go.

- I did not have much
background in machine learning,
but the resources provide to me internally
have been of great help.
- I've never been in a place
where you've learned so much
in such a short amount of time.
(upbeat music)
